flowchart TD
    A[State/Prop Change] --> B[Create New Virtual DOM]
    B --> C[Diff Against Previous Tree]
    C --> D{Element Type Changed?}
    D -- Yes --> E[Replace Subtree]
    D -- No --> F[Update Props]
    F --> G{List Uses Keys?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Match by Key]
    G -- No --> I[Match by Index]
    E --> J[Commit Updates to DOM]
    H --> J
    I --> J
